<section id="manufacturingDashboard" role="standard">
  <title><indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>dashboards</primary>
      <secondary>for manufacturing</secondary>
    </indexterm>Manufacturing Dashboard</title>
  <para>To view the Manufacturing Dashboard, select the "Dashboard" option.
  The following screen will appear:</para>
  <para><screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/manufacturingDashboard.png" />
        </imageobject>
        <caption>Manufacturing Dashboard</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot></para>
  <para>The Manufacturing Dashboard includes the following pre-loaded
  Dashboard Panes, which you can either remove or supplement with additional
  Panes at any time:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Work Orders Due</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Displays your Work Orders due this month.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Work Order Items Due</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Displays your Work Order items due this month.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Work Center Loading</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Displays your Work Center days capacity loading.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
  <xi:include href="../widgets/dashboardPane.xml" xpointer="dashboardsWidget"
              xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" />
</section>
